===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪʃəs|-ɪʃəs]]

===Adjective===
'''pernicious'''
#causing [[death]] or [[injury]]; [[deadly]]
#causing much [[harm]]; [[destructive]]
